values: 再次；再一次；再一遍；又一次；重复地；此外；而且；另外；另一方面；再说；再者；不过；然而（then again）

word_group.brief_definition: 重新考虑后另作打算(常指最终改变主意)
(尤指坏事)又开始了, 又一次发生了
出人意料地以新的活力重新出现
再次见你；再次见到你；又看到你
再来；再次来临；再次光临

bilingual.source: We tried to fix it once again.
bilingual.target: 我们再一次尝试修理它。

bilingual.source: I remind you to be careful once again.
bilingual.target: 我再一次提醒你要小心。
他们再一次讨论了这个问题。

bilingual.source: Once again, I'm sorry for the confusion and trouble caused.
bilingual.target: 再一次，我对造成的混乱和麻烦表示抱歉。

bilingual.source: I must prepare for the tests this time so that I won't fail again.
bilingual.target: 这次我必须为考试做准备，这样我就不会再一次不及格了。

bilingual.source: Once again, humans may be getting a helping paw or nose—from their best animal friends.
bilingual.target: 再一次，人类可能会从他们最好的动物朋友那里得到一只帮助性的爪子或鼻子。

bilingual.source: Once again disappointed, asks once again oneself, once again…
bilingual.target: 再一次失望，再一次问自己，再一次…

bilingual.source: Sukey, take it off again. Sukey, take it off again.
bilingual.target: 茶水壶，再一次把它拿走。 茶水壶，再一次把它拿走。

list.abstract: again是一个英文词汇，读音是【ə'gen】，可做副词用，表示“又；再”，源自古英语的ongean，意为朝向，反对。
韩国偶像团体T-ara的第八张迷你专辑《Again》，内收录了《NO.9》、《IKnowTheFeeling》等6首歌曲，其中作为双主打的《NO.9》和《IKnowTheFeeling》风格截然不同，前者为具有反转魅力的性感舞曲，后者则为充满画面感的中速情歌。

yingyinNormal.en: Captain Smek has saved us again!
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯迈克船长再一次救了我们！

yingyinNormal.en: But, Mum, I don't want to lose you again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是妈妈，我不想再一次失去你。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey! Once again, defeated by your own prurient interests.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再一次，你被你的恶趣味打败。

yingyinNormal.en: The kid with the two shirts screwed us again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那个长袖套短袖的小屁孩再一次祸害了我们。

yingyinNormal.en: We good? Yeah? Good? Once again, I pronounce you husband and wife. Now kiss her again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以吗？我要再一次，宣布你们结为夫妇，你可以再吻新娘一次。

yingyinNormal.en: And in a hopeful sign for middle-class families wages are on the rise again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 工资再一次上涨，这是给予中产家庭以希望的信号。

yingyinNormal.en: The Cricket Minister comes this way. His troops are mobilizing. War is upon us once again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 蟋蟀宰相正冲我们而来，他的军队整装待发，战争再一次降临。

yingyinNormal.en: Just like back in the old days. In short, we're gonna make Apple cool again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像我们在公司初创时做的那样。少而精，我们会让苹果再一次酷起来

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Hey. Oh, thanks again for letting me use your laptop last night. No problem. Was just doing my taxes. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨。再一次谢谢你昨晚借我用你电脑。没事。我就是上网报个税。好。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, you're ready? I'm gonna go in there with you. Thanks. You know just in case there's more than one dude in there with it. Again, Thanks. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你准备好了吗？我跟你一起进去。谢谢。以防里面不只有一个男的。再一次谢谢你。是啊。

yingyinNormal.en: On the Frabjous Day, when the White Queen once again wears the crown, on that day, I shall Futterwacken vigorously. Oh, no. Uh-oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等到辉煌之日，当白皇后再一次戴上皇冠之时，我会尽情展现我的福特沃肯舞的。哦，不。啊噢。

yingyinNormal.en: Once again, unbelievable. Yeah, once again, I know.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再次觉得你奇葩。再次回你，鹤立鸡群是谓奇葩。

yingyinNormal.en: Mon, Ethan called again. Mon? Mon? What? Ethan called again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莫妮卡，伊森又来电话了。什么？伊森又来电话了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, he looks sad again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他又看起来难过了。

yingyinNormal.en: Down to the docks again?
yingyinNormal.zh: 又要去码头了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And we will do so again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下次我们依然如此。

yingyinNormal.en: Why, is he teething again?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么，他又长牙了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Is he bothering you again?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他又在烦你吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Hi. Again. Hi. Hi. Hi. Hi.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好。又来了。你好。

yingyinNormal.en: Again, huge army of octopi.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别忘了，庞大的章鱼军队。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: These lessons are very important; they're how we grow, and how we keep from making that same mistake <highlight>again</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些教训非常重要；它们是我们成长的方式，也是我们避免再犯同样错误的方式。

examination_example.sentence: Today is no different, with academics, writers, and activists once <highlight>again</highlight> warning that technology is replacing human workers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今天也不例外，学者、作家和活动家再次警告说，技术正在取代人类工人。

examination_example.sentence: And I felt like that <highlight>again</highlight>, to a certain degree, when people responded to the blog so well.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在某种程度上，当人们对博客的反应如此之好时，我再次有了同样的感觉。

word_usage.usage: again作副词，用于“as + adj. + again"的结构时，表示“增加”。如：My brother is as old again as I am. 我哥哥的年龄比我大一倍。

examination_example.sentence: He also asked for unwanted bikes, which he would repair—<highlight>again</highlight> for free.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他还寻求没人要的自行车，他会修理——同样是免费的。

examination_example.sentence: I've taken so many Udemy courses, and ifs such a great feeling to get my brain working <highlight>again</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我上了很多Udemy的课程，能让我的大脑重新工作真是太棒了。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 重新考虑后另作打算(常指最终改变主意)

examination_example.sentence: Chinese mountain climbers got to the top of Qomolangma <highlight>again</highlight> in 2020!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2020年中国登山者再次登顶珠峰！

examination_example.sentence: I must prepare for the tests this time so that I won't fail <highlight>again</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这次我必须为考试做准备，这样我就不会再一次不及格了。

examination_example.sentence: The secretary apologized to the manager for making the same mistake <highlight>again</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 秘书因为再次犯了同样的错误而向经理道歉。

sense_info_list.en: showing that somebody/something is in the same place or state that they were in originally

examination_example.sentence: Because they are willing and patient to help Hally get strong <highlight>again</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为他们愿意并且有耐心帮助哈莉恢复健康。

examination_example.sentence: A year later, Nian came back <highlight>again</highlight>, but this time the lion couldn't help.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一年后，年又回来了，但这一次狮子帮不上忙。

examination_example.sentence: I want to come back <highlight>again</highlight> next year.

sense_info_list.en: added to an amount that is already there

examination_example.sentence: The network is expected to double in length <highlight>again</highlight>, to 70,000 kilometers, by 2035.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 预计到2035年，该网络的长度将翻倍，达到70000公里。

word_usage.usage: again不可与repeat等含重复意义的词连用。
